Workspace setContents: 'Display clear. Transcript show: ''HELLO''.'.
Workspace cursor moveToIndex: 1 line: 0 column: 8 topLine: 0.
Workspace selection collapseToLine: 0 column: 8.
(KernelInstaller objectNamed: 'BootWorkspaceEditorSurface')
    drawSource: Workspace contents
    status: 'READY'
    feedback: 'OUT> EDITOR COMPONENT'
    onForm: Display defaultForm.
Transcript show: 'EDITOR SURFACE'.
Transcript cr.
